  "keyFeatures": [
    "Define custom agents and environments with simple abstractions",
    "Unified interface for agent inference and training",
    "Asynchronous parallelized trajectory generation",
    "Scalable RL training with PPO, GRPO, and other algorithms",
    "Multiple training backends (verl, tinker)",
    "SDK for integrating LangGraph, SmolAgent, Strands workflows",
    "Support for LoRA fine-tuning and VLM training",
    "Multi-agent training workflows",
    "Built-in reward functions for code, math, and search tasks",
    "Distributed training support with Ray"
  ],
